{"tid":597462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國兩會】人代倡首艘國產航母以三國將領命名　稱證「台灣自古屬於中國」","createTime":"2018-03-18T16:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T08:02:30.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"2129dd182813e17bd880d50e031b690a757ea600","tid":597462,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:00:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【全國兩會】人代倡首艘國產航母以三國將領命名　稱證「台灣自古屬於中國」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180318/s00004/32728e5aaadc3cd21e94b54c0e07e20d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180318%2Fs00004%2F32728e5aaadc3cd21e94b54c0e07e20d.jpg&h=c4c08ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國首艘國產航母於去年4月下水，坊間估計軍方要花費兩年，進行舾裝及海試等後續工作，預計國產航母會在2020年服役。雖然距離服役仍有一段時間，但已有不少人大代表在此次兩會紛紛發表意見。當中，浙江台州市人大常委會主任元茂榮建議，國產航母未來可以三國時期吳國將領「衛溫」命名。<br />\n<br />\n元茂榮指，衛溫遠航台灣開疆闢土，是中國正史中關於大陸與台灣交往的最早紀錄。他又稱，衛溫這次遠航，比鄭和下西洋早1170多年，比哥倫布發現美洲新大陸早1260多年，堪稱世界航海史上的壯舉，其歷史地位與航母體現的海上強國的作用和力量是相通的。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，衛溫船隊往台灣開疆闢土做法，是國家和政府行為，這一歷史事實進一步表明台灣自古以來屬於中國。<br />\n<br />\n據史籍《資治通鑑》記載，吳主孫權因國內人力資源短缺之故，於公元230年派遣衛溫、諸葛直兩名將領，出海尋找夷州（傳現今台灣）和亶洲（傳現今日本），打算俘虜當地人為吳國所用。一年後，由於亶洲路途遙遠，兩人只能在中途返航，在夷州俘虜數千民眾回國交差。最後，孫權以勞師無功為由，將兩人下獄處死。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180318/s00004/1521362226549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180318%2Fs00004%2F1521362226549&d=Pvww11BRZGe2XT2%2BG%2FNVYzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bd92d34f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180318%2Fs00004%2F1521362226549&h=01c31f43\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180318/s00004/1521362226549</a>"},{"pid":"b93f7c2518fe3a0612d4b5693301843e52412946","tid":597462,"uid":49955,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"維穩號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330e9db001af27533512e9299925fce24688056b","tid":597462,"uid":33643,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"最後，孫權以勞師無功為由，將兩人下獄處死。<br />\n<br />\n好名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5fb77a15b0afef0d05d65aae068483bbf72070","tid":597462,"uid":171718,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"出完口宇術未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到悶"},{"pid":"c9b4882e56c1734cea84276ed904f08ab1bc5e04","tid":597462,"uid":171718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cf5fb77a15b0afef0d05d65aae068483bbf72070","tid":597462,"uid":171718,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"出完口宇術未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"出完口術未"},{"pid":"3f6e0cf207cc17395bfd8dbcf206fa9d488e798e","tid":597462,"uid":61660,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"330e9db001af27533512e9299925fce24688056b","tid":597462,"uid":33643,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"最後，孫權以勞師無功為由，將兩人下獄處死。<br />\n<br />\n好名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"其實係咪曲緊線<br />\n有個成功既鄭成功唔提"},{"pid":"1bc624ee0839d88f4abb934d9a4ba412fb7df492","tid":597462,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f6e0cf207cc17395bfd8dbcf206fa9d488e798e","tid":597462,"uid":61660,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"330e9db001af27533512e9299925fce24688056b","tid":597462,"uid":33643,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy